        </dd>

        
                <dt>Physical Descriptions</dt>
        <dd>
          <dl>
                          <dt>Medium</dt>
              <dd>Brown ink and brown and gray wash over black chalk on cream antique laid paper, partially squared in black chalk, partial framing line in brown ink, laid down on decorative mount</dd>
            
           
           
                          <dt>Dimensions</dt>
              <dd>sight: 25 x 31.5 cm (9 13/16 x 12 3/8 in.)</dd>
            
            
            
            
            
                          <dt>Inscriptions and Marks</dt>
              <dd>
                                  <ul class="unstyled-list">
                    
